{"tid":1960232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何栢良倡緊急立法強制市民公眾地方戴口罩","createTime":"2020-04-06T04:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T14:39:54.000Z","uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"07917d7d6693fdd46e99ecf8477f4bae3779de60","tid":1960232,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:31:25.000Z","msg":"何栢良倡緊急立法強制市民公眾地方戴口罩<br />\n3分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】限聚令及規管食肆的措施周末限期屆滿，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良預計，政府會延長有關措施，放寬機會「微乎其微」，又建議政府強制市民在公眾地方戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n他重申要規管食肆只提供外賣。<br />\n<br />\n對於博愛醫院的個案及警署內有警員確診，何栢良不排除是有人在醫院或工作地點不戴口罩，建議政府緊急立法強制市民在公眾地方戴口罩，又指「限聚令」已實施一星期，執法人員如發現違規應該立即執法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=386886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386886&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=0c496164\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386886&h=305d50e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=386886</a>"},{"pid":"b378fd7d09bf457f7518c04888b8f888b6966372","tid":1960232,"uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"雜種林鄭：上訴禁蒙面法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4715450d8eb8bc21a6a71a6c066e048abcb7089","tid":1960232,"uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"反反蒙面法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6a9a6ad8dfcd79c812148cfdb5f0e3c59c772c","tid":1960232,"uid":131157,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n又俾機會港共擴權"},{"pid":"37afe210fd9f9b8baa1025735363339b8def3f78","tid":1960232,"uid":141668,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"禁蒙面法仲上訴緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/do